QGroupBox {
  border: 1px solid gray;
  border-radius: 9px;
  margin-top: 0.5em;
}

QGroupBox::title {
  subcontrol-origin: margin;
  subcontrol-position: top center;
  padding: 0 3px;
}

/*
This will give your QGroupBox a gray border with rounded corners and a top margin.
The title of the group box will be centered at the top of the group box with a small amount of padding on either side.
*/